data.description: Come see this absolutely stunning home in the quiet subdivision of Block House Creek in the heart of booming Leander with convenient access to entertainment, shopping, major highways, restaurants and fantastic schools. Sturdy brick exterior, gorgeous cabinetry, granite counter tops, recent wood plank tile floors, and fresh paint cultivate the perfect canvas for your decor taste. Roomy bedrooms, large windows and high ceilings invite an open and airy feel throughout the home, complimented by the mature trees and massive backyard allowing ample space for entertaining guests at all your summer soirees. Also, a great little storage shed for tools, lawnmowers, etc. Oh, and did I mention no HOA and the wonderful community amenities? Schedule your private tour today!
